Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of bio-inspired Swarm Intelligence and Evolutionary Computation to create a self-organized Data-Mining system based on Stigmergic paradigms. This involves the use of local information to produce a global pattern, which is a common theme in the fields of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Swarm Intelligence (cs.SI). The paper also deals with Web usage data and World-Wide-Web Mining, which falls under the sub-categories of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC).
